Meta and the Quest Pro
----------------------

From The Verge ( https://www.theverge.com/2023/3/3/23622975/meta-quest-pro-=
2-price-cuts ) :

Mark Zuckerberg has announced that the Meta Quest Pro, the company=E2=80=99=
s mixed and virtual reality headset focused on business users, will be gett=
ing a substantial price cut, going from $1,499.99 to $999.99. Likewise, the=
 256GB version of the Quest 2 will be going from $499.99 to $429.99. Meta s=
ays its goal is to =E2=80=9Ccreate hardware that=E2=80=99s affordable for a=
