headset is getting a follow-up for at least a few years. Given that context=
, a price drop of this magnitude makes the most sense if the company=E2=80=
=99s trying to get rid of its existing inventory.

I agree. To the extent this price drop is about making the Quest Pro =E2=80=
=9Cavailable to even more businesses and professionals around the world=E2=
=80=9D that almost certainly is with the hope that someone buys this thing,=
 particularly before the next lower-end Quest headset comes out sometime th=
is year.

