ny is not planning to make a second Quest Pro headset. Andrew =E2=80=98Boz=
=E2=80=99 Bosworth announced Meta=E2=80=99s decision to not continue with i=
ts planned second-generation Quest Pro virtual-reality headset at the compa=
ny=E2=80=99s road map presentation, Alex Heath of The Verge reported in his=
