The company=E2=80=99s $1,499 Quest Pro has received mixed ( https://www.bus=
inessinsider.com/i-used-metas-virtual-reality-headset-in-office-in-metavers=
e-2022-12 ) to poor reviews ( https://www.theverge.com/23451629/meta-quest-=
