rtwatch-plans ) the company plans to continue developing three more Quest h=
eadsets over the next four years, with a Quest 3 headset set to release lat=
er this year. The headset is expected to be thinner but more powerful and e=
xpensive than the Quest 2.

I don=E2=80=99t necessarily think that the cancellation of future Quest Pro=
s indicates that Meta is stepping back from the Metaverse space; the most o=
bvious explanation is that Zuckerberg and company have come to agree with J=
ohn Carmack=E2=80=99s view that going high end was a mistake; from Ars Tech=
nica ( https://arstechnica.com/gaming/2022/10/carmack-wants-a-250-vr-headse=
